{"type":"answer","id":13688,"parentType":"question","parentId":2990,"uid":2115,"contents":"<b>这两位被枪毙之前,应该也是这么想的:虽然罗共确实有很多不足之处,但是有些人直接主张“推翻罗共”,那以后谁来管罗国?美国政府?苏联政府?救国阵线?还是教会?罗共灭亡了,你来管罗国啊?</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538135938845924.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538135938845924.jpeg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538135938845924.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>但是——革命胜利之后,罗马尼亚成功的进行了民主化改革,并于次年5月,举行了第一次大选。而就在齐奥塞斯库被推翻、枪毙仅仅几年之后,罗马尼亚的GDP,就开始高速增长。</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538136264122695.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538136264122695.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538136264122695.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>无独有偶,伊拉克的大独裁者萨达姆在临死之前,也大言不惭的说:“伊拉克没有了我萨达姆,将会一文不值!”</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538138605265643.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538138605265643.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538138605265643.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>后面的事情,我们就都知道了——萨达姆死后,伊拉克的经济,十年增长了八倍!</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538138702176070.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538138702176070.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180928/1538138702176070.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-09-28","agreeCount":24,"discussionCount":1}